items.checkin_comment: Fonzie Abbott - master of all trades. The Twin Palms is a reasonable pale ale, the dry-hopped process gives it plenty of flavour for a 4.5% ABV beer. You end up with something quite light in profile, very easy drinking and what I find to be a malty finish
